data.description: Here is your chance to own a beautiful Cape in the Endwell School District. This house has plenty of old world charm giving it that "cottage" feel. Situated on a little over 1/3 acre it gives you plenty of room for the outdoors.  This house has a finished lower level with a full bath and a "summer kitchen". Situated on a quiet dead end street with plenty of room for parking in the driveway.  Don't let this one slip away. Call your favorite REALTOR for an appointment.
